author: COMSOL
description: Experiments on dry and wet soil samples are performed to understand their behavior under different loading conditions. In this example, the Extended Barcelona Basic (BBMx) soil model is used to simulate the wetting and drying paths in partially saturated soil samples under cyclic loading.
label: wetting_and_drying_of_unsaturated_soil.mph
